-- Miller Group Appoints Philip Bowman as Chairman
-- B y   R o s s   L a r s e n
-- 2012-04-23T09:27:22Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-23/miller-group-appoints-philip-bowman-as-chairman-correct-.html
(Corrects to say Bowman remains Smiths Plc chief
executive.)  Philip Bowman has been appointed
Chairman of Miller Group Ltd. effective today, the company said
in the statement. Bowman, 59, is the chief executive of  Smiths
Group Plc (SMIN)  and was formerly chief executive of Scottish Power
Plc. He succeeds Brian Stewart.  To contact the reporter on this story:
